``` nix
# configuration.nix
programs = {
  gnupg.agent = {
    enable = true;
    enableSSHSupport = true;
    pinentryPackage = pkgs.pinentry-dmenu;
  };
};
```

you can also see available pinentry programs for nixos [here](https://search.nixos.org/packages?channel=25.11&query=pinentry). since we choose `pinentry-dmenu` then we also need to specify that package in our `system packages`

``` nix
systemPackages = with pkgs; [
  pinentry-dmenu
];
```
